					<a href="https://buy.stripe.com/7sI1845N20x1gUg7st" class="btn"
		target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
		>
						Split Payment
					</a>

					<a href="https://buy.stripe.com/bIY2c86R693xfQc5km" class="btn"
		target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
		>
						Pay in Full
					</a>
				</div>
			</article>

			<p class="center">Pay in full or choose the option to pay half at checkout, with the remaining balance due by April 1, 2025.</p>
