						lessons into your daily life.
					</p>
				</li>
				<li>
					<p>
						<b>Luxury accommodations: </b> Stay in a serene and stylish luxury accommodations with private bedrooms and bathrooms, sauna, hot tub and a forest located directly behind the retreat home.
